          &lt;/ports&gt;
          &lt;wait&gt;
            &lt;time&gt;10000&lt;/time&gt;
          &lt;/wait&gt;
        &lt;/run&gt;
      &lt;/image&gt;
    &lt;/images&gt;

It sets the runtime FTP user (see section Setting runtime FTP user of the [readme](https://github.com/stilliard/docker-pure-ftpd) and password.You need to open the `30000-30009` ports to make [ftp passive mode](https://stackoverflow.com/q/1699145/8482479) work. 

